-31T13:04:27.000Z","msg":"快d實名出黎啦，我唔想見到以下o既野發生：<br />\n<br />\n好多毅進仔想結婚生仔，所以先去做警察<br />\n因為o係香港，佢地無可能靠實力搵到咁高人工<br />\n佢地自己係爛命一條，但可以為仔女放棄好多<br />\n你地千祈唔好係警察宿舍隔離引入大媽舞<br />\n唔好咁早就唱歌、大力從高處掉野然後四散<br />\n唔好整爆屎渠<br />\n唔好玩人電話<br />\n唔好跟蹤人地老婆仔女<br />\n唔好向佢地年幼子女傳教畫畫講警察做左d咩<br />\n唔好杯葛人地老婆仔女<br />\n<br />\n去純警察宿舍好啦，暫時唔好連累其他紀律部隊<br />\n<br />\n去警察宿舍附近歡迎咁多位勞苦功高o既警員<br />\n佢地無gear,  只能隻揪，夠公平<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最緊要：真休班警無OT</span></span><br />\n出去趕人只可做義工<br />\n然後訓幾個鐘又要返工<br />\n仲要可能周圍好嘈，<br />\n嘈醒老婆仔女黎嘈醒佢<br />\n慘<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6c1fae38278fef2e2cc978ae244df342903028d","tid":1391333,"uid":76699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:04:29.000Z","msg":"三萬狗得500個親屬想笑大我個口咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0536b638a579f3c80dbf91a908910286dc575fe4","tid":1391333,"uid":14567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:04:42.000Z","msg":"頂唔順咪辭職囉"},{"pid":"93eae3974535056145ac2bfe7d814a02d31bfe6f","tid":1391333,"uid":17399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:04:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c62f32a29c4b20725a27b6489b66bc9214a3fe5","tid":1391333,"uid":44174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:05:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4577354eb95750129ac7d25cae0f2ee723966505","tid":1391333,"uid":109437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:05:17.000Z","msg":"禍必及<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"806786cd12ff24998df53269cdeda9038893ecdf","tid":1391333,"uid"